data.description: Great 4 Bedroom Home with 3 baths, and lots of space. Enjoy the openness of the living, dining and kitchen. Stainless appliances in large kitchen with breakfast island. opens to large, screened porch.  The lower level has L-shaped family room with brick fireplace, bath, bedroom and utility room.  The roof and siding are approx. 3 years old. Privacy fenced yard approx. 1 year ago.  There is an FHA assumable loan at 3.25%.
